GAS: Recyling system is up and running with a total gas flow of 30l/h, system is not bubbling. We found and fixed a gas leak yesterday evening, we consumed about 8kg of gas during the day, there is 4kg left in the bottle but decided to switch bottle in order not to go out of gas overnight. After the gas leak we use about 2kg of gas in 8h.

 

To be continued...we go for lunch
